<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cancellation Policy - Stayzio</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.7/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-LN+7fdVzj6u52u30Kp6M/trliBMCMKTyK833zpbD+pXdCLuTusPj697FH4R/5mcr" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 0 60px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fe424d 0%, #ff6b73 100%);
            color: white;
            margin: -20px -20px 40px;
            border-radius: 0 0 30px 30px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><circle cx="20" cy="20" r="2" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/><circle cx="80" cy="40" r="1.5" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/><circle cx="40" cy="80" r="1" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/><circle cx="90" cy="80" r="2.5" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/></svg>') repeat;
            animation: float 20s infinite linear;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0% { transform: translate(0, 0); }
            100% { transform: translate(-100px, -100px); }
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            opacity: 0.9;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .content {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .policy-section {
            margin-bottom: 35px;
            padding: 25px;
            border-left: 4px solid #fe424d;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(254,66,77,0.05) 0%, transparent 100%);
            border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .policy-section:hover {
            transform: translateX(5px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(254,66,77,0.15);
        }

        .policy-section h2 {
            color: #fe424d;
            font-size: 1.4em;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .policy-section h3 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            margin: 20px 0 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .policy-section p, .policy-section li {
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .policy-section ul {
            margin-left: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .highlight {
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, rgba(254,66,77,0.1) 0%, rgba(254,66,77,0.05) 100%);
            padding: 15px 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            border: 1px solid rgba(254,66,77,0.2);
        }

        .important-notice {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fe424d 0%, #ff6b73 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .important-notice::before {
            content: '⚠️';
            font-size: 2em;
            position: absolute;
            top: 10px;
            right: 20px;
            opacity: 0.3;
        }

        .contact-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 2px solid rgba(254,66,77,0.1);
        }

        .contact-info {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            margin: 0 15px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .contact-info:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .icon {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            fill: #fe424d;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 10px;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 25px;
            }
            
            .policy-section {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .header {
                margin: -10px -10px 30px;
            }
            
            .logo {
                font-size: 2em;
            }
            
            .contact-info {
                display: block;
                margin: 10px 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo"><i class="fa-solid fa-earth-asia brand-icon"></i>Stayzio</div>
            <div class="subtitle">Cancellation Policy</div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="important-notice">
                <strong>Important:</strong> Please read our cancellation policy carefully before making a reservation. This policy applies to all bookings made through Stayzio.
            </div>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>
                    <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.58L19 8l-9 9z"/>
                    </svg>
                    Free Cancellation
                </h2>
                <div class="highlight">
                    <p><strong>48+ Hours Before Check-in:</strong> Cancel free of charge and receive a full refund.</p>
                </div>
                <p>You can cancel your reservation up to 48 hours before your scheduled check-in time without any penalties. The full amount will be refunded to your original payment method within 5-7 business days.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>
                    <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path d="M11.99 2C6.47 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.47 10 9.99 10C17.52 22 22 17.52 22 12S17.52 2 11.99 2zM12 20c-4.42 0-8-3.58-8-8s3.58-8 8-8 8 3.58 8 8-3.58 8-8 8zm.5-13H11v6l5.25 3.15.75-1.23-4.5-2.67z"/>
                    </svg>
                    Moderate Cancellation
                </h2>
                <h3>24-48 Hours Before Check-in</h3>
                <p>Cancellations made between 24-48 hours before check-in will incur a <strong>50% cancellation fee</strong>. You will receive a refund of 50% of the total booking amount.</p>
                
                <h3>Less than 24 Hours Before Check-in</h3>
                <p>Cancellations made less than 24 hours before check-in are subject to a <strong>100% cancellation fee</strong>. No refund will be provided.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>
                    <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
                    </svg>
                    Special Circumstances
                </h2>
                <p>We understand that unexpected situations may arise. The following circumstances may qualify for exceptions to our standard cancellation policy:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Medical emergencies (documentation required)</li>
                    <li>Natural disasters or severe weather conditions</li>
                    <li>Government-imposed travel restrictions</li>
                    <li>Flight cancellations by airlines (proof required)</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Please contact our support team with appropriate documentation for review.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>
                    <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path d="M20 6h-2.18c.11-.31.18-.65.18-1a2.996 2.996 0 0 0-5.5-1.65l-.5.67-.5-.68C10.96 2.54 10.05 2 9 2 7.34 2 6 3.34 6 5c0 .35.07.69.18 1H4c-1.11 0-1.99.89-1.99 2L2 19c0 1.11.89 2 2 2h16c1.11 0 2-.89 2-2V8c0-1.11-.89-2-2-2zm-5-2c.55 0 1 .45 1 1s-.45 1-1 1-1-.45-1-1 .45-1 1-1zM9 4c.55 0 1 .45 1 1s-.45 1-1 1-1-.45-1-1 .45-1 1-1z"/>
                    </svg>
                    Refund Processing
                </h2>
                <p>All eligible refunds will be processed according to the following timeline:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Credit/Debit Cards:</strong> 5-7 business days</li>
                    <li><strong>Digital Wallets:</strong> 1-3 business days</li>
                    <li><strong>Bank Transfers:</strong> 7-10 business days</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="highlight">
                    <p><strong>Note:</strong> Refunds are processed to the original payment method used for booking. Processing times may vary depending on your financial institution.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>
                    <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm1 17h-2v-2h2v2zm2.07-7.75l-.9.92C13.45 12.9 13 13.5 13 15h-2v-.5c0-1.1.45-2.1 1.17-2.83l1.24-1.26c.37-.36.59-.86.59-1.41 0-1.1-.9-2-2-2s-2 .9-2 2H8c0-2.21 1.79-4 4-4s4 1.79 4 4c0 .88-.36 1.68-.93 2.25z"/>
                    </svg>
                    How to Cancel
                </h2>
                <p>You can cancel your reservation through any of the following methods:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Log into your Stayzio account and go to "My Bookings"</li>
                    <li>Contact our customer support team</li>
                    <li>Use the cancellation link in your booking confirmation email</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="highlight">
                    <p><strong>Important:</strong> Cancellation requests must be submitted through official Stayzio channels. Cancellations requested through property owners or third parties may not be processed according to this policy.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="contact-section">
                <h2 style="color: #fe424d; margin-bottom: 20px;">Need Help?</h2>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; color: #666;">Our customer support team is available 24/7 to assist you with cancellations and refunds.</p>
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 15px;">
                    <div class="contact-info">
                        <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path d="M20 4H4c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L2 18c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h16c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V6c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 4l-8 5-8-5V6l8 5 8-5v2z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>support@stayzio.com</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="contact-info">
                        <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path d="M6.62 10.79c1.44 2.83 3.76 5.14 6.59 6.59l2.2-2.2c.27-.27.67-.36 1.02-.24 1.12.37 2.33.57 3.57.57.55 0 1 .45 1 1V20c0 .55-.45 1-1 1-9.39 0-17-7.61-17-17 0-.55.45-1 1-1h3.5c.55 0 1 .45 1 1 0 1.25.2 2.45.57 3.57.11.35.03.74-.25 1.02l-2.2 2.2z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>+91-9920694680-STAYZIO</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This cancellation policy was last updated on September 8, 2025. Stayzio reserves the right to modify this policy at any time.</p>
            <p>© 2025 Stayzio. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>